### hello.cpp

```cpp
#include <iostream>

int main() {
    std::cout << "Hello CheatSheets\n";
    return 0;
}
```

Compiling and running

```shell script
$ g++ hello.cpp -o hello
$ ./hello
Hello CheatSheets
```

