namespace ns1 {int val(){return 5;}}
int main()
{
    std::cout << ns1::val();
}
```

---

```cpp
#include <iostream>
namespace ns1 {int val(){return 5;}}
using namespace ns1;
using namespace std;
int main()
{
    cout << val();
}
```

Namespaces allow global identifiers under a name

