int add(int a, int b) {
    return a + b;
}

int main() {
    std::cout << add(10, 20);
}
```

`add` is a function taking 2 ints and returning int

### Overloading

```cpp
void fun(string a, string b) {
    std::cout << a + " " + b;
}
void fun(string a) {
    std::cout << a;
}
