```

Permanent `301` redirect

```php
Route::permanentRedirect('/here', '/there');
```

### Regular Expression Constraints 

```php
Route::get('/user/{name}', function ($name) {
    //
})->where('name', '[A-Za-z]+');

Route::get('/user/{id}', function ($id) {
