### Examples 

#### Reverse records

```
awk -F: '{ x[NR] = $0 }
    END {
        for (i = NR; i > 0; i--)
        print x[i]
    }
' /etc/passwd
```

#### Reverse fields

```
awk -F: '{
    for (i = NF; i > 0; i--)
        printf("%s ",$i);
    print ""
}' /etc/passwd
```

#### Sum by record

```
awk -F: '{
    s=0;
    for (i = 1; i <= NF; i++)
        s += $i;
    print s
}' /etc/passwd
```

#### Sum whole file

```
awk -F: '
    {for (i = 1; i <= NF; i++)
        s += $i;
    };
    END{print s}
' /etc/passwd
```

