awk 'BEGIN {
    while (a < 10) {
        print "- " " concatenation: " a
        a++;
    }
}'
```

#### do...while

```
awk '{
    i = 1
    do {
        print $0
        i++
    } while (i <= 5)
}' /etc/passwd
```

